    • Uses of SVGTransform in de.bkroeger.myvisio.svg

      Classes in de.bkroeger.myvisio.svg that implement SVGTransform 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  SVGTransformImpl
      Many of SVG's graphics operations utilize 2x3 matrices of the form: [a c e] [b d f] which, when expanded into a 3x3 matrix for the purposes of matrix arithmetic, become: [a c e] [b d f] [0 0 1]
      Methods in de.bkroeger.myvisio.svg that return SVGTransform 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      SVGTransform SVGTransformListImpl.consolidate()
      Consolidates the list of separate SVGTransform objects by multiplying the equivalent transformation matrices together to result in a list consisting of a single SVGTransform object of type SVG_TRANSFORM_MATRIX.
      SVGTransform SVGTransformListImpl.createSVGTransformFromMatrix(SVGMatrix matrix)
      Creates an SVGTransform object outside of any document trees.
